NZ food price index rises 0 . 4 pct in Aug . Statistics New Zealand on Thursday released the following data for the Food Price Index for August : Aug 1996 July 1996 Aug 1995 + 0 . 4 pct + 0 . 1 pct + 0 . 2 pctyr - end Aug 1996 yr - end July 1996 yr - end Aug 1995 + 2 . 4 pct + 2 . 2 pct + 0 . 7 pctNote - The index makes up 18 percent of the consumer price index ( CPI ) . Economists had forecast the index would rise 0 . 5 percent in August to give an annual rise of 2 . 5 percent . 
